				<h2>About the Author, <a href="http://venturebeat.com/author/dean-takahashi/" title="Posts by Dean Takahashi">Dean Takahashi</a></h2>
				<p>
				Dean is lead writer for GamesBeat at VentureBeat. He covers video games, security, chips and a variety of other subjects. Dean previously worked at the San Jose Mercury News, the Wall Street Journal, the Red Herring, the Los Angeles Times, the Orange County Register and the Dallas Times Herald. He is the author of two books, Opening the Xbox and the Xbox 360 Uncloaked. Follow him on Twitter at <a href="http://www.twitter.com/deantak">@deantak</a>, and follow VentureBeat on Twitter at <a href="http://www.twitter.com/venturebeat">@venturebeat</a>.				</p>
		</div><!--END author-block-->
			
